&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engage deeply in the veterinary and canine health community&lt;/strong&gt; — becoming a trusted thought leader and a credible, compassionate advocate for dogs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Champion fresh canine nutrition&lt;/strong&gt; — helping veterinary teams discover how fresh, personalized nutrition can revolutionize dog care—aiding in disease management, wellness, and improving quality of life.&lt;/li&gt;
